column1: SPF Brute Strength Powerlifting and Bench Press Classic Results

Results for 2/20/10 Brute Strength Powerlifting and Bench Press Classic  I want to personally thank Stella Kapinski, all the Judges, Loader/Spotters, Announcer and score keeper for putting on a perfectly ran event. I also want to than the Brute Strength Gym and staff for hosting the event. It was a pleasure to meet and work with everyone. Thanks to all the lifters and spectators that came out and took part in this event, you people are what makes the events and you are also what makes the SPF what it is today. Thanks everyone and hope to see you again in Nov. at the Virginia State Powerlifting and Bench Press Championship, Stella will be posting a date very soon.                              SPF President: Jesse Rodgers
